	(text "MOC3063M Peak Surge Current: 1A\nRprotection = ACpeak/1A = 325/1 => 360ohm\nPr = (Vt-Vphoto)²/R\nVt = Vphoto + R*Igtriac = 3 + 360*0.05 = 21V\nPr = (21-1.8)²/360 = 1W\nwe will use 3 0.5W resistor in parallele to dissipate the power\noriginal design was with BTA16-600BW which have a 50mA Igt,\nBTA16-600CW have a 25mA Igt. We keep worst case at 50mA"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 168.402 78.74 0)
		(effects
